{"to":["sarah@alumni.prestige.edu"],"subject":"Quick Update on the New Admissions Cycle","body":"Hi Sarah,

I hope you’re doing well!

I wanted to share a quick snapshot of the latest admissions cycle at Prestige:

• Applications are up 5% year-over-year, reaching a record 15,000.
• With selectivity continuing to rise, the acceptance rate has tightened to 7%, resulting in 1,050 outstanding admits.
• Academic strength remains impressive – the incoming class averages a 1480 SAT and a 33 ACT.
• Our community is more global than ever, with students arriving from 60+ countries.

The energy on campus is already palpable as we begin welcoming this remarkably diverse cohort. I’ll keep you posted as orientation and yield events unfold, but let me know if there’s anything specific you’d like to hear more about.

Thanks for staying connected to Prestige!

Best,
[Your Name]
Admissions Office"}

formatted_items.content: Email sent to Sarah with the key highlights of the new admissions cycle. Let me know if you’d like any other details shared.
